      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine is incredibly smooth, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every feature functions exactly as intended. It has been meticulously maintained and garage-kept, making it an ideal choice for a collector or anyone seeking a vehicle in showroom-quality state.",
