    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention to be roadworthy, as the engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with heavy paint fading and several large dents. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears and the electronics are inconsistent. This would be a major project for an experienced mechanic or a source for spare parts.",
