    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to disciplined ownership and mechanical care. This specimen exhibits a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a refined driving experience. While it displays the expected character of a pre-owned executive transport, its structural integrity and aesthetic presentation remain superior. This offering represents a sophisticated acquisition for the professional seeking a reliable, high-performance asset without the premium of a showroom-new price tag.",
      "price": 31500.0,
