      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one! I've taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for some new adventures. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2013 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features the 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) with Drivelogic, providing instantaneous shifts and rev-matching downshifts. The mechanical suite includes the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damping Control (EDC), ensuring the chassis maintains composure under high lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes an inspection of the rod bearings and replacement of the throttle actuators, ensuring the individual throttle bodies operate with precision. The suspension bushings and subframe mounts remain firm, preserving the communicative steering feel this platform is known for. While the car shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with a well-loved driver's example, its powertrain and drivetrain performance remain exceptionally sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
