    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect blend of reliability and refined aesthetics. The exterior retains a brilliant, deep luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, while the carpets and headliner are in excellent condition. Every feature, from the premium audio system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control, operates perfectly. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent fluid service and brake inspection already completed. It shifts smoothly, accelerates with purpose, and provides a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a high-quality, well-documented vehicle that is ready for immediate daily use or long-distance touring.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
